{"tid":2214814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"惠譽：滙控及渣打面臨美國制裁風險增","createTime":"2020-09-23T13:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T15:15:08.000Z","uid":21470,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9cac8b85c204468417ef075eeaca964e3d2185a7","tid":2214814,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:45:32.000Z","msg":"惠譽：滙控及渣打面臨美國制裁風險增<br />\n<br />\n評級機構惠譽發表報告，認為在中港有龐大業務的非美資銀行，包括滙控和渣打，面臨被美國制裁風險升溫。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽表示，中資銀行及與中國有聯繫的非美資銀行，可能在未來幾個月面臨華府調查，華府將列出涉及與損害香港主權的組織有巨額交易的海外金融機構清單，而考慮到雙邊貿易和投資風險，以及中國政府可能報復，預計不會對中資銀行有實質性制裁，但中資或港資銀行可能被限制與美國的聯繫，這些銀行大部分在美國的在岸業務，只佔整體業務一小部分。惠譽又說，現時沒有跡象顯示美國銀行會從中國撤資，但預計美國銀行將承受更大壓力，加大審查以美元結算或融資的中港金融機構。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2358615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2358615&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9jv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=a3b8cc8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2358615</a>"},{"pid":"7e4fe9003251106b3748eeb64790b3944a52b27a","tid":2214814,"uid":5929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:46:04.000Z","msg":"15!"},{"pid":"98e35e976beb5ac66ff9d57eec614a684bb8e4ff","tid":2214814,"uid":280329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61d9a3ba2e2ae032348e4665a086fb000d34f01","tid":2214814,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:47:41.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e54ea45d4c7b6a7cd55d2f0bd7c166601bf09f6","tid":2214814,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T13:48:19.00